      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRUNSWICK ROCKET (4) dropped out early but wound up strongly and charged into the minors when a 4 length third (22.13) at this track in Grade 5. The form out of last race has been strong. Can measure up this time. ARKA SOLAR (5) sprung the lids and on speed throughout before being run over late when fifth (22.38) at this track over 390m. Bold showing expected. RICOCHET RIPPLE (2) has good early dash but last time was shuffled out the back and missed the frame, finishing seventh (22.36) in a Grade 3/4 at this track. Fast away and won (22.36) at this track the start prior. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Should be thereabouts. MAYWYN'S LUCK (1) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
